title: Trump endorses John E. Sununu in New Hampshire Senate race over Scott Brown
description: Trump’s support would once have been hard to imagine for the moderate critic of his. Now it further boosts Sununu as the GOP aims to flip an open Senate seat.
content: Trump’s support would once have been hard to imagine for the moderate critic of his. Now it further boosts Sununu as the GOP aims to flip an open Senate seat.
